Python:-
Is an object oriented, dynamic-typed language. 
Created by Guido van Rossam during his college days. 
It's executed line-by-line. 
Free Open-source language.
For GUI devlopment, Tkinter lib can be use. 
Python can be used in large of things, like web development, Data Science, Security, Machine Learning, COmputer Vision, Automation, Artificial Intelligence, IoT. 

Python IDE:-
Choose anyone, Jupyter notebook, Anaconda or PyCharm

